snippet.title: Swift: FB Messenger - Core Data Entities: Create, Read, Delete (Ep 2)
snippet.description:
In today's video, we learn how to power our list of recent messages using Core Data.  First we define our Entity objects, generate the necessary NSManagedObject subclass files.  Next we manually create a few messages and friends using NSEntityDescription.

Finally we load our UICollectionView with a list of these message objects.

(Part 1) Auto Layout Using Code or Programmatically: https://youtu.be/XtEoKixIfG4

Download Completed Project:
https://www.letsbuildthatapp.com/course/Facebook-Chat-Messenger
